Conways Game of Life (by Justin)
=======================================
Controls:

p - Puases the simulation
delete - clears the whole board
q or esc - exits the program
left mouse button - makes a live cell
right mouse button - kills a live cell
=======================================

=====================================================
Compile:

make


(the command is simply for reference)
g++  -o ConwaysGameofLife SDLText.cpp `sdl-config --cflags --libs`
(with g++)
=====================================================
